### Define Dexie.js Export Progress Interface

Source: https://github.com/dexie/dexie.js/blob/master/addons/dexie-export-import/README.md

Defines the TypeScript interface for `ExportProgress`, which is passed to the `progressCallback` during a Dexie export operation. It provides details on the total and completed tables and rows, and a `done` flag.

```ts
export interface ExportProgress {
  totalTables: number;
  completedTables: number;
  totalRows: number;
  completedRows: number;
  done: boolean;
}
```

